 salt and pepper and chop <b>5 sec\/speed 6<b>. Mix with aid of spatula and repeat chopping if required."},{"content":"Remove string from roulades and slice, top slices with reserved sun-dried tomato paste."},{"content":"Serve with mint pea mash."}],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","35m","4 portions"]}